  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"ibuxpK0x\">还有<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=760464508&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E7%89%A9%E7%A7%8D%E8%AE%A4%E7%9F%A5%E9%9A%9C%E7%A2%8D&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">物种认知障碍<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>。</p><p data-pid=\"pkgEVbLc\">说一个人一直认为自己是只老鼠，所以家人送他去看医生。医生终于给他治好了，但是让他回家，他不走。</p><p data-pid=\"9fBAqdkN\">因为他对医生说:“我现在知道自己不是只老鼠了，可是你得让门外的猫也知道啊!”</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
